h" title="Lucy Mack Smith">Lucy <i>Mack</i> Smith</a><br /><small>1776–1856</small></div></td></tr><tr style="height:1px;text-align:center"><td style="border-right:1px solid black;height:1em;width:1em"></td><td style="height:1em;width:1em"></td></tr>
