0–1844)</small></div></td><td colspan="2" style="height:1em;border-bottom:1px dashed black;width:2em"></td><td colspan="6" rowspan="2" style="border:0px solid black;padding:0.2em"><div class="center" style="width:auto; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:EmmaSmith.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/EmmaSmith.jpg/50px-EmmaSmith.jpg" decoding="async" width="50" height="79" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/EmmaSmith.jpg/75px-EmmaSmith.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/EmmaSmith.jpg/100px-EmmaSmith.jpg 2x" data-file-width="318" data-file-height="500" /></a></span><br /><a href="/wiki/Emma_Hale_Smith" class="mw-redirect" title="Emma Hale Smith">Emma Hale Smith</a><br /><small>1804–1879<br />Elect Lady</small></div></td><td colspan="6" rowspan="2" style="border:0px solid black;padding:0.2em"><div class="center" style="width:auto; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Williamsmith.gif" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Williamsmith.gif/50px-Williamsmith.gif" decoding="async" width="50" height="67" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Williamsmith.gif/75px-Williamsmith.gif 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Williamsmith.gif/100px-Williamsmith.gif 2x" data-file-width="179" data-file-height="240" /></a></span><br /><a href="/wiki/William_Smith_(Latter_Day_Saints)" title="William Smith (Latter Day Saints)">William B. Smith</a><br /><small>1811–1893<br />Presiding Patriarch<br />(1845)</small></div></td></tr><tr style="height:1px;text-align:center"><td style="border-right:1px solid black;height:1em;width:1em"></td><td style="height:1em;width:1em"></td></tr>
