anized Church of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints</a> (Community of Christ)</div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%"><a href="/wiki/Succession_crisis_(Latter_Day_Saints)" title="Succession crisis (Latter Day Saints)">Pre-succession crisis</a></th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em"></div><table class="nowraplinks navbox-subgroup" style="border-spacing:0"><tbody><tr><th id="President" scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%"><a href="/wiki/President_of_the_Church#President" title="President of the Church">President</a></th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">J. Smith Jr.</a> (1830–44)</li></ul>
